      "content": "talking to a counselor doesnt change the numbers. it doesn't change the fact that i'm a complete fraud. i built this whole life on nothing and now everyone knows. the debt is just a permanent stain on my name. i feel like there's just this massive, heavy darkness over everything. it's like the only way to actually stop the feeling is to just stop existing.",
